high_descs: Turn left and face the coffee maker.
Take the mug out of the coffee maker.
Step left to go in front of the fridge.
Place the mug in the fridge, close the door, wait a moment, and then take the mug back out.
Take a step left and face the coffee maker again.
Place the mug back in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled mug in a coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn to your left and face the coffee machine
Pick up the coffee mug from the coffee machine
Turn right and walk over to the refrigerator and open it
Place the coffee mug on the shelf next to the apple. Close the fridge. Open the fridge back up and pick up the coffee mug.
Close the fridge and turn left. Walk over and stand in front of the coffee machine
Place the coffee mug back in the coffee machine
anns.task_desc: Grab the mug from the coffee machine. Put inside the refrigerator. Put it back in the coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the coffee maker.
Pick up the black up on the coffee maker.
Take a step to the right to face the fridge.
Open the fridge, place the cup next to the apple, let the cup cool down, and take it back out of the fridge.
Take a step to the left to face the coffee maker.
Place the cup back on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Cool down the cup on the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn and take a step closer to the coffee maker.
Pick up the mug from the base of the coffee maker.
Carry the mug to the fridge on your right.
Open the fridge, place the mug on the top shelf on your left, close the door, and then remove after a couple seconds.
Turn to your left and take the mug back to the coffee maker.
Place the mug on the base of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled mug on the coffee maker.

high_descs: turn to the left to face the coffee maker
pick up the black mug from inside the coffee maker
turn right, walk to fridge, face the fridge
open the fridge doors, place mug on the left shelf next to the apple, close doors, wait for mug to chill, open doors, pick up black mug
turn left, walk to the coffee maker on counter, turn to face coffee maker
place black mug inside coffee maker
anns.task_desc: chill a black mug for the coffee maker

high_descs: Turn left to face the coffee maker.
Pick up the black cup from the coffee maker.
Turn right, walk towards the fridge, and face the fridge.
Open the fridge, place the cup next to the apple, close the fridge, wait a moment, open the fridge and get the cup out.
Turn left and walk towards the coffee maker and face it.
Put the cup back on the coffee maker.
